        options: ["Beta-blockers can worsen coronary vasospasm by leaving alpha-mediated vasoconstriction unopposed","Beta-blockers are not available in the formulary for cardiac conditions","Beta-blockers only work for high blood pressure, not angina","Both medications are equally effective; amlodipine was chosen randomly"],
        correct: 0,
